Use the standard library
This is how to sort_third of l:
   Remember that thirds is []
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this l's length times:
      When remainder of i and 3 is 0, then:
         Add thirds to item i in l
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   Remember that a is 0
   Do this thirds's length times:
      Remember that b is 0
      Do this thirds's length times:
         When item a in thirds is less than item b in thirds, then:
            Remember that temp is item a in thirds
            Remember that item a in thirds is item b in thirds
            Remember that item b in thirds is temp
         End when
         Increase b
      End do
      Increase a
   End do

   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that j is 0

   Do this l's length times:
      When remainder of i and 3 is 0, then:
         Add result to item j in thirds
         Increase j
      But, if not:
         Add result to item i in l
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is result
